
Observations

1.) View tasks abstractly to clearly communicate the data
2.) Designers should create tools that the user uses to abstract the data
3.) This method is used to try and discover new ideas from data that has been abstracted
4.) Multiple end goals for data abstraction. Science, knowledge, or for enjoyment to see data visualized
5.) Can be used for searching complex data sets, allows passive browsing of the data for interesting data points


